data.description: Welcome to this charming 2-story single-family home nestled in a tranquil neighborhood. Boasting 4 bedrooms, including a spacious primary suite on the 1st floor, this home offers comfort and convenience for every family member. The primary suite's bathroom is a true retreat, featuring 2 vanity sinks, a generously sized garden tub, a separate walk-in shower and walk-in closets provide plenty of storage space for your wardrobe and belongings. This home features crown molding gracing every room. The well-appointed kitchen showcases beautiful granite countertops, making meal preparation a breeze. Step outside to discover a fully fenced backyard, perfect for outdoor gatherings and play, complete with a screened-in lanai for bug-free relaxation. The major appliances and roof are only 7 years old, ensuring worry-free living. Upstairs, a spacious living area connects all the bedrooms, creating an ideal space for a playroom or office. Residents of this community enjoy a wealth of amenities, including a refreshing pool, a separate children's pool, a playground, a fully-equipped gym, and sports facilities like basketball and tennis courts. Schedule your showing today!
